WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.300 --> 00:00:02.800
I want you, don't be ignorant

2
00:00:03.100 --> 00:00:04.400
Mr. Shen has a crush on you

3
00:00:04.400 --> 00:00:05.733
That's your blessing.

4
00:00:05.733 --> 00:00:07.333
Don't be alone because of you

5
00:00:07.333 --> 00:00:08.800
The Ye family and Shen Yuan were implicated

6
00:00:09.066 --> 00:00:10.500
It's not that you don't know

7
00:00:10.500 --> 00:00:13.266
What is our Ye family like now?

8
00:00:13.266 --> 00:00:14.666
You can't always look at us

9
00:00:14.666 --> 00:00:16.400
Let's go beg for dinner

10
00:00:16.400 --> 00:00:18.633
But your Ye family is to blame

11
00:00:18.733 --> 00:00:19.800
As for Shen Yan

12
00:00:20.300 --> 00:00:21.500
I warn you

13
00:00:21.500 --> 00:00:22.866
Who dares to move?

14
00:00:22.866 --> 00:00:24.666
I won't let you go if I'm a ghost

15
00:00:26.600 --> 00:00:27.866
We'll see about that.

16
00:00:31.800 --> 00:00:32.600
Wife

17
00:00:33.200 --> 00:00:34.900
Honey, I'm back.

18
00:00:34.900 --> 00:00:35.933
Stop barking

19
00:00:35.933 --> 00:00:38.066
Your wife has been dedicated by me

20
00:00:38.133 --> 00:00:40.100
Someone who is truly worth having

21
00:00:40.566 --> 00:00:43.200
The boss of the other party is very generous

22
00:00:43.200 --> 00:00:45.200
Also sold for a good price

23
00:00:45.333 --> 00:00:46.400
Pardon me?

24
00:00:46.866 --> 00:00:48.366
Qin Shao said

25
00:00:48.366 --> 00:00:51.066
Your wife was sold. Do you understand?

26
00:00:51.300 --> 00:00:53.166
Do you want to know who I sold it to?

27
00:00:54.066 --> 00:00:55.066
How about this one?

28
00:00:55.066 --> 00:00:57.966
It's the letter that the lord asked me to give you

29
00:00:58.600 --> 00:01:01.466
Ah, you better kneel now

30
00:01:01.466 --> 00:01:03.366
Please forgive me for your previous actions

31
00:01:03.466 --> 00:01:06.333
Otherwise, you will never want to pick up the leaf problem in your life.

32
00:01:06.333 --> 00:01:07.633
Kneel down

